609
00:28:52.740 --> 00:28:54.820
Jeez. how can you say that?

610
00:28:54.820 --> 00:28:56.500
How can I do that to you?

611
00:28:56.500 --> 00:28:58.740
We're all direct disciples of Master.

612
00:28:58.740 --> 00:28:59.460
