643
00:29:57.580 --> 00:29:58.780
Qualified for?

644
00:29:59.300 --> 00:30:01.660
To inherit Tianshidu.

645
00:30:10.420 --> 00:30:12.860
Why should I be here

646
00:30:12.860 --> 00:30:15.420
