670
00:31:04.900 --> 00:31:05.580
And the murderer...

671
00:31:05.580 --> 00:31:06.940
Stop.

672
00:31:07.620 --> 00:31:09.260
I've heard this before.

673
00:31:09.260 --> 00:31:10.260
You mean to tell me

674
00:31:10.260 --> 00:31:12.020
