724
00:33:07.780 --> 00:33:10.140
But I'm approaching the three-year period.

725
00:33:10.140 --> 00:33:11.660
It's going to succeed soon.

726
00:33:11.660 --> 00:33:12.540
Qi Apotheosis

727
00:33:12.540 --> 00:33:14.820
