767
00:35:28.460 --> 00:35:30.140
Are you doing some cosplay thing?

768
00:35:30.460 --> 00:35:31.700
Let me tell you.

769
00:35:32.340 --> 00:35:33.140
I'm

770
00:35:33.140 --> 00:35:35.260
