771
00:35:35.260 --> 00:35:36.260
I have a class tomorrow.

772
00:35:36.260 --> 00:35:37.300
Bye. then.

773
00:35:37.300 --> 00:35:38.420
Martial Uncle.

774
00:35:43.660 --> 00:35:44.940
Don't waste your effort

775
00:35:44.940 --> 00:35:46.220
