794
00:37:01.420 --> 00:37:02.420
Jiyun. Yexing.

795
00:37:03.140 --> 00:37:04.260
Back off.

796
00:37:04.260 --> 00:37:05.300
Martial Uncle.

797
00:37:05.820 --> 00:37:06.380
This fellow simply can't...

798
00:37:06.380 --> 00:37:07.460
I said. back off.

799
00:37:16.580 --> 00:37:17.140
What

800
00:37:17.140 --> 00:37:17.940
